            "title": "今日我咁睇｜美伊局勢緊張 影響全球股市 港股料調整｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MTY2DbIvWnQEv1Xxk7S7UA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/ad112b644cbcfdf1ae49280af1215614\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.農曆新年期間，主要事件是以色列備戰，市場憂慮一旦美伊談判不理想，戰事即一觸即發，油價亦創近年新高，通脹加地緣政治憂慮，影響市場的整體氣氛。此外，聯儲局理事米蘭，作為特朗普的支持者，近期指料減息或有所放慢，聯儲局減息的速度或再影響，同樣左右股市表現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.今年暫時來看，似乎都以物理AI為主題，大型科網公司注定要燒錢，市場憂慮AI投資回報不如理想，因此港股如阿里巴巴、騰訊，美股如微軟及谷歌等，作為燒錢大戶都要被沽貨，至於AI大模型股份，則表現相當好。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ecf46cb0-016c-38fa-ab6f-d8bc6cba5410-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 今日北水缺席，預計港股要隨外圍氣氛轉弱下跌，資源股考慮到減息步伐減慢，可能要有一輪調整，大家小心為上，或者選AI大模型股份。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4. 港股短期阻力位再下降至26200點及26000點，考慮到幾隻科網藍籌表現極弱，估計下周下試26000點的機會甚大，看情況再考慮是否於26000點買入。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證迫近八成的水平，如上期所言，挾牛的機會高，暫時來看，基本因素及相反理論，兩方面都支持大市要進一步向下。</p></div>",
